name: shelly
title: No time to explain!
description: Shelly's spread-fire shotgun blasts the other team with buckshot. Her Super destroys cover and keeps her opponents at a distance!

name: nita
title: The Untamed
description: Nita strikes her enemies with a thunderous shockwave. Her Super summons a massive bear to fight by her side!

name: colt
title: The Pretty
description: An unlikely hero that often finds himself in the wrong place at the right time. He's not one to shy away from a mirror and is simply brimming with confidence!

name: bull
title: Bulldozer!
description: Bull deals massive damage up close with his shotgun. For his Super move, he charges through barriers and knocks back enemies!

name: brock
title: Boom!
description: When Brock's not lighting up the battle with rockets, he's lighting up the dance floor with his smooth moves.

name: elprimo
title: El Luchador
description: El Primo throws a flurry of punches at his enemies. His Super is a leaping elbow drop that deals damage to all caught underneath!

name: barley
title: You got served!
description: Barley readily serves up the finest beverages in Starr Park. Dirty his bar though and steam comes out and bottles start flying!

name: poco
title: El Mariachi
description: Poco fires damaging sound waves at enemies. His Super can heal both Poco himself and his teammates!

name: rosa
title: Touching Grass
description: This boxing botanist will plant her feet and go toe to toe! Her Super gives her tough, vegan protective gear.

name: jessie
title: The Builder
description: Jessie's Shock Rifle shoots energy orbs that bounce between enemies. Her Super deploys a cute but deadly gun turret!

name: dynamike
title: Birdie, birdie, birdie!
description: Long thought lost deep down a mine. Mad Dynamike is back - and he's still itching to blow everything to smithereens!

name: tick
title: Where's my head?
description: Tick is a metal ball of barely controlled excitement and energy - explosive energy! He throws mines, and his Super makes his head detach, seek a target and explode.

name: 8bit
title: SYS 64738
description: 8-Bit lumbers along like an arcade cabinet on legs. He shoots Blaster Beams and his Super boosts friendlies' damage!

name: rico
title: The Lover
description: Rico fires a burst of bullets that bounce off walls. His Super burst is a long barrage of bouncy bullets that pierce targets!

name: darryl
title: Pirrrate!
description: Darryl has a powerful double-shotgun attack. His Super move is a reckless roll inside his bouncy barrel!

name: penny
title: The Salty
description: A rebel without a cause, mischievous Penny rules the high seas. She's a bonafide menace on the lookout for adventure and will stop at nothing for plunder.

name: carl
title: The Geologist
description: Carl throws his Pickaxe like a boomerang. His Super is a crazy cart spin that clobbers anyone around him.

name: jacky
description: Jacky works her Jackhammer to shake up the ground and nearby enemies. Her Super pulls in nearby foes, leaving them in the dust!

name: gus
title: The Lost
description: Hanging out in a long forgotten and abandoned train ride, Gus loves balloons. He's a master at crafting balloon animals, which he uses to pass the time and to keep himself company.

name: bo
title: One with Nature
description: Bo fires three explosive arrows toward his targets. His Super ability places a trio of hidden, explosive mines on the ground!

name: emz
title: #haters
description: Emz attacks with blasts of hair spray that deal damage over time, and slows down opponents with her Super.

name: stu
title: Wicked
description: Stu is a stunt driver extraordinaire with gasoline in his veins! He makes a big entrance, burning serious rubber all over the stage.

name: piper
title: The Sniper
description: Piper's sniper shots do more damage the farther they travel. Her Super drops grenades at her feet, while Piper herself leaps away!

name: pam
title: Your mom
description: Pam shoots from the hip, peppering targets with shrapnel. Her Super is a healing turret that restores her and teammates' health!

name: frank
title: The Tank
description: Frank swings his hammer at enemies, sending a shockwave. His Super is an especially powerful blow that stuns enemies!

name: bibi
title: Cool Cat
description: Batter up! Bibi's got a sweet swing that can knock back enemies when her Home Run bar is charged. Her Super is a bouncing ball of gum that deals damage.

name: bea
title: Queen
description: Bea loves bugs and hugs. She shoots her mechanical drones at range, and her Super sends forth an angry army of swarming bees!

name: nani
title: Nanny
description: Nani loves her friends and looks over them with a watchful lens. She handles threats with angled shots, and her Super allows Nani to commandeer her pal Peep, who goes out with a bang!

name: edgar
title: CEO of Brawl Stars
description: Edgy and with a hands-off attitude, Edgar prefers to throw punches with his scarf. With his Super, Edgar jumps into the fray swinging his scarf around himself.

name: griff
title: The Greedy
description: Griff is the proprietor of Starr Park's gift shop. Business is bad, but he still throws coins away - from his employees' tip jar!

name: grom
title: With one left hand!
description: Watchman Grom's priority is to keep guard. He throws his trusty radio at his enemies. His Super is a big bad bomb that breaks walls and pushes back enemies!

name: bonnie
title: The Reckless
description: Bonnie and her inanimate cannon Clyde are usually up to no good. Who would have thought that this cute little girl would cause so much mayhem?

name: hank
title: Lil' Tenant
description: Compensating much? Hank is rarely seen outside his over-sized tank.

name: mortis
title: Creature of the Night
description: Mortis dashes forward with each swing of his shovel. As his Super attack, he sends a cloud of bats to damage enemies and heal himself!

name: tara
title: What's in the cards?
description: What's in the cards for you? This mystic from a far land has come to read your fortune. It says simply: DEFEAT!

name: gene
title: Talk to the Hand!
description: Gene uses his magic lamp to shoot a splitting projectile. His super is a magical hand that grabs and pulls enemies close!

name: max
title: I AM SPEED!
description: Max goes fast! Her attack is a fast-firing blaster. Her Super speeds up her and allies!

name: mrp
title: The Boss
description: Mr. P is a disgruntled luggage handler who angrily hurls suitcases at opponents. His Super calls robo-porters to help him.

name: sprout
title: Tree hugger
description: Sprout was built to plant life, launching bouncy Seed Bombs with reckless love. Its Super creates a plant-based obstacle!

name: byron
title: The Sensational
description: Byron deals with potent medicaments, but never call him a snake oil salesman!

name: squeak
title: is an accident
description: As Col. Ruff's accidental creation, Squeak was born to play fetch!

name: gray
title: The Shady
description: What's the meaning of Orthochromatic? Gray would tell you, but he doesn't speak much.

name: willow
title: Is in your head!
description: Lovable? Maybe. Frightening? Without a doubt. Controlling? 100%.

name: spike
title: One of a Kind
description: Spike throws cactus grenades that send needles flying, and a show-stopping Super: a field of cactus spines that slows down and damages enemies!

name: crow
title: Caw caw!
description: This enigmatic creature just appeared in town one day. Nobody dares to ruffle his feathers - not anymore.

name: leon
title: The Sneaky
description: Leon shoots a quick salvo of blades at his target. His Super trick is a smoke bomb that makes him invisible for a little while!

name: sandy
title: The Sleepy
description: Sandy is a sleep-deprived Brawler with powerful control over sand: casting sharp pebbles at enemies, and summoning a sandstorm to hide teammates.

name: amber
title: Fire Starter
description: Amber has always been a firebug. She loves to light up the world and any opponents that come at her!

name: meg
title: Tech Support 2.0
description: Meg has a basic form and an advanced form where she hops inside her trusted Mecha suit. The suit gradually loses health, returning Meg to her basic form when the Mecha suit is destroyed.

name: chester
title: Jack of all Trades
description: What's in the box? Limitation of Liability: Under no circumstances shall Starr Corporation or its affiliates, partners, suppliers or licensors be liable for any indirect, incidental, ...

name: gale
title: The Janitor
description: Gale is a tireless handyman who gets no rest. With his blower, he blasts foes with a wide shot of wind and snow, while his Super pushes them back with a forceful blizzard!

name: surge
title: Bro
description: He's a Protector with a penchant for parties. Surge attacks foes with energy drink blasts that split in two on contact. His Super upgrades his stats in 3 stages and comes complete with totally awesome body mods!

name: colette
title: The Collector
description: Colette is going to get you! She taxes opponents' health and has fancy moves to boot.

name: lou
title: is here for you!
description: Lou is a cool guy, literally! He can dole out all kinds of chill stuff. But watch your step on the ice, and be careful not to get brain freeze!

name: ruffs
title: Colonel
description: He may bark orders at his subordinates, but Colonel Ruffs is a very good boy! Possessing a serious and calm demeanor, Ruffs keeps his dog traits hidden, unless there's a game of fetch going on!

name: belle
title: Starr
description: Belle inspires adoration in her gang, while her Electro-Rifle brings shock and awe to any opponent!

name: buzz
title: Born bad
description: Buzz is the lifeguard at Velocirapids. He constantly scans for folks in trouble he can throw his torpedo buoy to, but his throws are rather overenthusiastic.

name: ash
title: Trash Tier
description: Ash easily gets furious about all the junk he has to clean up. Dealing or receiving blows, even more so. The Fury makes him faster and more dangerous, but eventually he cools down.

name: lola
title: Drama Queen
description: Part guide and part actress and full diva, Lola is THE leading lady of Brawlywood. She attacks with her scarf and her Super is a channeled manifestation of her Ego.

name: fang
title: Sneaker Artist
description: Fang kicks first and he kicks fast. His main attack is a hefty kick that sends his shoe flying! Fang's Super is a powerful kick that will chain hit multiple enemies who are close together.

name: eve
title: Mother
description: Eve believes that everyone can be valuable... as a resource for her babies.

name: janet
title: The Rocket
description: Janet is the star of the show, and she's not afraid to let everyone around her know about it. If only her sister Bonnie wouldn't constantly get into trouble...

name: otis
title: The Artist
description: Otis is a street artist who chills in the deep with his starfish pal Cil. Together they throw up graffiti pieces all over Starr Park.

name: sam
title: In your face!
description: A former factory hand, Sam Bronson has a vendetta against ALL robots. He's the brawn behind the brains of the Goldarm Gang, always happy to take the loot and give robots the boot!

name: buster
title: Blockbuster
description: Operating the projector at the movie theater, Buster has his favorite action movies memorized. He dreams to someday become an action hero in his own blockbuster movie.

name: mandy
title: Tough Cookie
description: If you feel low on sugar, drop by Mandy's Rainbow Candy Shop. Remember kids - you'll always feel dandy with Mandy's Candy!

name: rt
title: The Watcher
description: Lost in Starr Park? No worries, friend! R-T is watching you! Erm, no. He's watching OVER you. Yes. That. Totally.

name: maisie
title: Master of Disaster
description: POP POP POP! Is that popcorn or enemies succumbing?
